{"tid":544404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"呂麗瑤遭性侵︰警方昨日在機場拘捕男教練","createTime":"2018-01-29T12:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T06:53:56.000Z","uid":31048,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"93663544fb14592331b258a738238367e79d84e9","tid":544404,"uid":31048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:55:08.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=5of6%2Frr%2Bxs%2F2k3BnJCQvUF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=91c27bcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】香港體壇去年驚爆性侵醜聞，有「香港欄后」之稱的港隊田徑跨欄女將呂麗瑤，趁去年11月30日凌晨踏入23歲生日，於社交網站Facebook發貼，披露在未成年時曾遭男教練性侵犯。警方經調查後，昨日在機場以涉嫌非禮拘捕一名返港男子。疑犯報稱不適，需送院治理，目前留醫北大嶼山醫院。"},{"pid":"5784e01c38c24ceac767125f42fb2b9833627083","tid":544404,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:56:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1173eca803d1708e71d5abeeee226418a3d0c031","tid":544404,"uid":135074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428f92c875f4bb42a156abe457fd1ae7d4f69493","tid":544404,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54f4f0004b0d1b00fce6831b868fab6633104ff8","tid":544404,"uid":31048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T00:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e47fdf1deb0a127448f896cf56f2f45d6e0f19a","tid":544404,"uid":44457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T00:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid